flowchart TD
  PM[Polymarket Orderbooks] --> IN[Ingest & Normalize]
  DR[Deribit Orderbooks + Index] --> IN
  IN --> RAW[(Raw Store)]
  IN --> DB[(Postgres)]
  DB --> MAP[Mapping Service]
  MAP --> PR[Pricing: BS + CDF]
  PR --> SIG[Signal Engine]
  SIG --> EXE[Execution Plan]
  SIG --> API[Signals API]
  EXE --> API
